Barbell Bench Press – 4x8

Incline Dumbbell Press – 4x10

Chest Dips or Machine Dips – 3x12

Cable Flyes – 3x15

Push-ups (burnout set)

Day 2: Back

Deadlifts – 4x6

Pull-ups – 4x10 (or Lat Pulldown)

Barbell Rows – 4x8

Seated Cable Rows – 3x12

Face Pulls – 3x15

Day 3: Shoulders

Overhead Barbell Press – 4x8

Lateral Raises – 4x12-15

Rear Delt Flyes – 4x12

Front Plate Raises – 3x12

Shrugs – 3x15

Day 4: Arms (Biceps + Triceps)

Barbell Curls – 4x10

Preacher Curls – 3x12

Concentration Curls – 3x12

Close-Grip Bench Press – 4x10

Skull Crushers – 3x12

Tricep Rope Pushdowns – 3x15

Day 5: Legs

Squats – 4x8

Romanian Deadlifts – 4x10

Leg Press – 3x12

Walking Lunges – 3 sets (each leg)

Hamstring Curls – 3x15

Calf Raises – 4x20

Day 6: Chest + Arms (Pump Day / Volume Focused)

Incline Machine Press – 4x15

Pec Deck – 3x20

Dumbbell Curls – 3x15

Hammer Curls – 3x15

Cable Tricep Pushdowns – 3x20

Rope Overhead Extensions – 3x15

Finisher: Superset Push-ups & Curls to failure

Day 7: Rest or Active Recovery
